The '''Jamaican nationality law''' is governed by the Law on Citizenship of [[Jamaica]] (the ''Jamaica Citizenship Act''), and by the [[Constitution of Jamaica|Jamaican Constitution]].
== Dual Citizenship == Jamaican law allows their citizens to hold [[dual citizenship]].
