'''Shevu'ot''' or '''Shevuot''' ([[Hebrew language|Hebrew]]: שבועות, "Oaths") is a book of the [[Mishnah]] and [[Talmud]]. It is the sixth volume of the book of [[Nezikin]]. Shevu'ot deals primarily with the laws of [[oath]]s in [[halakha]] (Jewish law).

